mil.emp3.api.enums

Enum IconSizeEnum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<IconSizeEnum>
      • mil.emp3.api.enums.IconSizeEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IconSizeEnum>

    public enum IconSizeEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<IconSizeEnum>
    This class enumerate the icon sizes suported by the system. Actual pixel size is not used do to the difference in pixel density of android devices.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      LARGE
      This enumerated value indicates a size equivalent to 1.8 the size of a SMALL icon.
      MEDIUM
      This enumerated value indicates a size equivalent to 1.4 the size of a SMALL icon.
      SMALL
      This enumerated value indicates a size equivalent to a 1/3 in X 1/3 in icon.
      TINY
      This enumerated value indicates the smallest size possible.
